</div>
<p class="mt-1 text-[10px] italic text-slate-500">The built-in norm table ships empty on purpose — a benchmark line renders only after each value is verified against its primary source (see the Benchmark workspace below). Until then, adding one politely refuses rather than showing an unverified number.</p>
<div class="mt-3 flex items-center gap-2 flex-wrap">
